msph.landingPage.thirdPartySoftware.page.paragraph1: The MoonSphere system uses the following OpenSource libraries for serving multiple different functionalities. If you hover over a library and click on the link, you will be redirected to the GitHub repository page. You can find all the libraries' licenses
msph.landingPage.thirdPartySoftware.page.paragraph2: If you are interested in how the MoonSphere system is built, its purpose and how it works from the development side, you can find more information
